---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Yashodhan Deshmukh — Lead Product Designer with 15+ years of experience.">
  <div class="container">

    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="page-header__label">About</p>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">Yashodhan Deshmukh</h1>
      <p class="page-header__desc">
        Lead Product Designer. 15+ years turning complex systems into
        things people actually want to use.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="bio">
      <p>
        I believe the best design is invisible — it just works. My approach combines
        strong product thinking with storytelling-driven design.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently, I'm the founder and lead designer of
        <a href="https://order.law" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Order.law</a>,
        an AI-powered legal research platform. Before that, I led design at Zeni AI,
        Bajaj Finserv, and Globant — working across fintech, enterprise, and SaaS.
      </p>
      <p>
        Strong advocate for scalable design systems and the kind of cross-functional
        collaboration that actually moves products forward.
      </p>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <section>
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Skills</p>
      <div class="skills-block">
        <div>
          <p class="skill-group__heading">Product Design & Strategy</p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Product Design</span>
            <span class="tag">UX</span>
            <span class="tag">Interaction Design</span>
            <span class="tag">Information Architecture</span>
            <span class="tag">Design Systems</span>
            <span class="tag">Wireframing</span>
            <span class="tag">Prototyping</span>
            <span class="tag">Usability Testing</span>
            <span class="tag">Product Strategy</span>
            <span class="tag">User Research</span>
            <span class="tag">Data-Driven Design</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="skill-group__heading">Tools & Technologies</p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Figma</span>
            <span class="tag">Sketch</span>
            <span class="tag">Adobe Creative Suite</span>
            <span class="tag">HTML</span>
            <span class="tag">CSS</span>
            <span class="tag">JavaScript</span>
            <span class="tag">Google Analytics</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <section>
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Experience</p>

      <div class="timeline">

        <div class="timeline__item">
          <div class="timeline__left">
            <p class="timeline__period">Oct 2024<br/>Present</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline__right">
            <p class="timeline__role">Founder & Lead Product Designer</p>
            <p class="timeline__company">Order.law</p>
            <ul class="timeline__points">
              <li>Designed and built an AI-powered legal research platform end-to-end — concept to launch.</li>
              <li>Led product design, front-end development, and API integration in a two-person team.</li>
              <li>Built the information architecture, search experience, and design system from scratch.</li>
              <li>1.13M search impressions, 24.6K clicks, avg. Google ranking position 8.6.</li>
              <li>Grew platform to 28K users and converted 3 law firms into 25+ paid subscribers.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline__item">
          <div class="timeline__left">
            <p class="timeline__period">Jun 2022<br/>Aug 2024</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline__right">
            <p class="timeline__role">Lead Product Designer</p>
            <p class="timeline__company">Zeni AI</p>
            <ul class="timeline__points">
              <li>Led design for an AI-powered financial operations platform — accounting automation and financial reporting.</li>
              <li>Managed and mentored a team of 8 designers across product, engineering, and ops.</li>
              <li>Designed complex financial dashboards to simplify workflows for finance teams and founders.</li>
              <li>Introduced data-driven design practices and contributed to the company design system.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline__item">
          <div class="timeline__left">
            <p class="timeline__period">Jan 2021<br/>May 2022</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline__right">
            <p class="timeline__role">Lead Product Designer</p>
            <p class="timeline__company">Bajaj Finserv</p>
            <ul class="timeline__points">
              <li>Led design for consumer durables finance, rural term loans, gold loans, and B2B/B2C platforms.</li>
              <li>Owned the full design process — research, IA, interaction design, prototyping, and testing.</li>
              <li>Explored emerging technologies (AI, AR, blockchain) for future product capabilities.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline__item">
          <div class="timeline__left">
            <p class="timeline__period">Jan 2018<br/>Jan 2021</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline__right">
            <p class="timeline__role">Sr. User Experience Designer</p>
            <p class="timeline__company">Globant</p>
            <ul class="timeline__points">
              <li>Designed enterprise digital products for global clients across product, engineering, and business.</li>
              <li>Facilitated design workshops and story mapping sessions to translate requirements into UX.</li>
              <li>Partnered with engineering to evaluate feasibility and deliver high-quality product experiences.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline__item">
          <div class="timeline__left">
            <p class="timeline__period">Aug 2012<br/>Oct 2017</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline__right">
            <p class="timeline__role">Sr. Associate Design</p>
            <p class="timeline__company">Synechron Technologies</p>
            <ul class="timeline__points">
              <li>Designed UX for financial and enterprise products working with PMs, engineers, and stakeholders.</li>
              <li>Produced design documentation — functional requirements, site maps, and process flows.</li>
              <li>Spot Award recipient for 5 consecutive years for consistent performance and delivery.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <div class="two-col">
      <section>
        <p class="section__eyebrow">Education</p>
        <div class="edu-list">
          <div>
            <p class="edu-item__title">Master of Arts</p>
            <p class="edu-item__sub">University of Pune · 2019–2021</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="edu-item__title">Bachelor of Arts</p>
            <p class="edu-item__sub">University of Pune · 2013–2017</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="edu-item__title">Diploma in Web Design</p>
            <p class="edu-item__sub">Edit Institute · 2009–2010</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <p class="section__eyebrow">Achievements</p>
        <div class="edu-list">
          <div>
            <p class="edu-item__title">Heroes Award</p>
            <p class="edu-item__sub">Bajaj Finserv — product capabilities across multiple digital assets.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="edu-item__title">Excellence in Work</p>
            <p class="edu-item__sub">Globant — two large-scale enterprise projects delivered in one month.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="edu-item__title">Spot Award × 5</p>
            <p class="edu-item__sub">Synechron Technologies — five consecutive years of consistent performance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
